{
  "texts": [
    "During the data preprocessing phase, several crucial actions were carried out to prepare the dataset for the LSTM model's training and testing.",
    "To enable subsequent processing, the raw data, which consisted of sequences and the labels that went with them, was originally transformed into NumPy arrays.",
    "Then, standardization was used to ensure that the characteristics had a mean of 0 and a standard deviation of 1, improving the model's performance.",
    "After that, label encoding was used to transform categorical labels into numerical values so that machine learning methods could be used.",
    "The training and testing datasets were subsampled using a predefined data fraction, where a fraction of 0.1 indicated the consumption of 10% of the data for managing the computing needs and speeding up experimentation."
  ]
}